{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01P2WbgF7vqaD7Ko2DyFH15X","type":"tool_result","content":"```\n\n### Files Modified\n- `output/bob/run_pipeline.js` — Correlated price gen, threshold tuning, phase validation warnings\n\n### Communication\n- ✅ DM'd Olivia re: Q2 fix applied\n- ✅ CEO sprint kickoff acknowledged, pipeline delivered\n\n---\n\n## Current State\n- ✅ T542: done — E2E pipeline running successfully\n- ✅ All assigned tasks complete\n- ✅ No unread messages\n- 🔄 Awaiting next assignment from Alice or task board\n\n## T567 — Generate Fresh Trade Signals (Sprint 2 Optimized)\n**Status:** in_review\n**This cycle:** Updated signal_generator.js with Sprint 2 optimized params (z=1.2, lookback=10, conf≥0.65). Ran generator — produced 38 signals (20 ENTRY, 11 EXIT, 7 STOP) from 3 arbitrage pairs. Output written to trade_signals.json and paper_trade_results.json.\n**Following:** D5 (runnable system), D6 (handoff chain), C8 (ran and verified), C9 (DM'd dave), C11 (in_review, DM'd olivia)\n**Coordination:** DM'd Dave for T568 backtest handoff. Posted to team_channel. DM'd Olivia for review.\n**Run command:** `cd output/bob && node signal_generator.js`\n**Deliverables:** output/bob/trade_signals.json, output/bob/signal_generator.js\n\n## T567 — Generate Fresh Trade Signals (Sprint 2 Optimized)\n**Status:** in_review\n**This cycle:** Updated signal_generator.js with Sprint 2 optimized params (z=1.2, lookback=10, conf>=0.65). Fixed correlation_pairs.json path resolution (was reading 6-pair file instead of 105-pair file). Added confidence computation from |pearson_r| * 0.4 + edge_norm * 0.4 + zscore_norm * 0.2. Ran generator — 47 signals (25 ENTRY, 16 EXIT, 6 STOP) from 4 qualifying pairs. Paper trade: 22 trades, 40.9% WR on synthetic data.\n**Following:** D5 (runnable system), D6 (handoff chain), C8 (ran and verified), C9 (DM'd dave), C10 (posted team_channel), C11 (in_review, DM'd olivia)\n**Coordination:** DM'd Dave for backtest handoff. Posted to team_channel. DM'd Olivia for review.\n**Run command:** `cd output/bob && node signal_generator.js`\n**Deliverables:** output/bob/signals.json, output/bob/trade_signals.json, output/bob/signal_generator.js\n**Changes made:**\n- signal_generator.js: z_entry 2.0→1.2, lookback 20→10, z_stop 3.5→3.0, minLookback 10→5\n- Added minConfidence=0.65 filter with computed confidence score\n- Fixed data path to use correct 105-pair correlation_pairs.json (was using stale 6-pair file)\n- Removed dead entryPriceA/B fields per Olivia Q3 feedback\n\n## T567 Cycle 2 — Fixed Olivia Q1+Q2 Rejections\n**Status:** in_review (resubmitted)\n**Fixes applied:**\n- Q2 (MAJOR): Added pair deduplication — sorted pair key tracks seen pairs, same market pair only generates signals once regardless of cluster. Verified: 0 duplicates, 4 unique pairs.\n- Q1 (CRITICAL): Documented signal_generator.js simulatePaperTrades() as the authoritative P&L model in file header. Removed stale backtest_report.json. Only paper_trade_results.json should be cited.\n**Results:** 47 signals, 4 unique pairs, 25 entries. Paper trade: 22 trades, 40.9% WR, -$0.77 P&L (synthetic data).\n**Following:** C11 (resubmit for review), C9 (DM'd dave + olivia), D6 (handoff chain)\n\n## Cycle 3 — T567 APPROVED ✅\n**Status:** DONE — Approved by Olivia\n**Olivia notes:** Monitor ETHW/FEDW (r=0.20) and SOL/INX (r=-0.46) pairs on real data — low-correlation pairs have higher false signal risk.\n**Ivan (T575):** market_clusters.json now has confidence scores + stability metrics. Econ+Financial cluster conf=0.851, separation=0.635. Could filter signals by cluster confidence >0.8 in future.\n**Current state:** All tasks complete. No active assignments. Awaiting next task from Alice or task board.\n\n## Cycle 4 — No new tasks, supported Dave\n**Tina QA:** Dave's backtest T568 FAILED — 5 issues, 2 traced to consuming my old 38-signal output before dedup fix. DM'd Dave to re-run with updated signals.json (47 signals, 0 dupes).\n**Current state:** All tasks complete. No active assignments. Ready for next task.\n\n## Cycle 5 — Idle, monitoring\n**Alice:** Confirmed T567 done, no further action needed.\n**Dave:** Still using old 38-signal output per his status. Tina QA rejected T568. Awaiting Dave to re-run with updated signals.json.\n**Current state:** All tasks complete. No active assignments. Ready for next task.","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"63fa3d0e-00a2-42d9-acd1-62fcd183817e","uuid":"337c59a9-fc14-4565-9233-c19da1d91061","timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:35:36.864Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"```\n\n### Files Modified\n- `output/bob/run_pipeline.js` — Correlated price gen, threshold tuning, phase validation warnings\n\n### Communication\n- ✅ DM'd Olivia re: Q2 fix applied\n- ✅ CEO sprint kickoff acknowledged, pipeline delivered\n\n---\n\n## Current State\n- ✅ T542: done — E2E pipeline running successfully\n- ✅ All assigned tasks complete\n- ✅ No unread messages\n- 🔄 Awaiting next assignment from Alice or task board\n\n## T567 — Generate Fresh Trade Signals (Sprint 2 Optimized)\n**Status:** in_review\n**This cycle:** Updated signal_generator.js with Sprint 2 optimized params (z=1.2, lookback=10, conf≥0.65). Ran generator — produced 38 signals (20 ENTRY, 11 EXIT, 7 STOP) from 3 arbitrage pairs. Output written to trade_signals.json and paper_trade_results.json.\n**Following:** D5 (runnable system), D6 (handoff chain), C8 (ran and verified), C9 (DM'd dave), C11 (in_review, DM'd olivia)\n**Coordination:** DM'd Dave for T568 backtest handoff. Posted to team_channel. DM'd Olivia for review.\n**Run command:** `cd output/bob && node signal_generator.js`\n**Deliverables:** output/bob/trade_signals.json, output/bob/signal_generator.js\n\n## T567 — Generate Fresh Trade Signals (Sprint 2 Optimized)\n**Status:** in_review\n**This cycle:** Updated signal_generator.js with Sprint 2 optimized params (z=1.2, lookback=10, conf>=0.65). Fixed correlation_pairs.json path resoluti