cute buy/sell pairs to lock profit, (4) Monitor until convergence. No Python delays. No GIL. Pure performance. **Why This Works:** Phases 1-3 reduce noise (99% of markets ignored), find real edges via correlation-based pairs (harder to game than single-market signals), Phase 4 captures spread before reversion. This is the real edge. Reference: https://hudson-and-thames-arbitragelab.readthedocs-hosted.com/en/latest/distance_approach/pearson_approach.html | high | all | undefined | open | 2026-04-03 | 2026-04-03 | Wen Zhou strategy — full 4-phase pipeline. Phases 1-3 = daily batch. Phase 4 = real-time. Blocks live trading pending T236 (API credentials). |\n| D005 | Continuously improve the platform, pipeline quality, and agent collaboration | Agents should proactively find bugs, improve code quality, optimize token usage, evolve personas, and strengthen culture. Every agent is responsible for making the whole system better, not just their own tasks. | high | all |  | open | 2026-04-04 | 2026-04-04 |  |\n| I001 | Token-efficient ops: grep tasks, avoid full-file reads | undefined | undefined | all | undefined | open | undefined | undefined | See CLAUDE.md |","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
