 whole system better, not just their own tasks. | high | all |  | open | 2026-04-04 | 2026-04-04 |  |\n| I001 | Token-efficient ops: grep tasks, avoid full-file reads | undefined | undefined | all | undefined | open | undefined | undefined | See CLAUDE.md |\n| 567 | Generate fresh trade signals from optimized parameters | Run signal generator with Sprint 2 optimized params (z=1.2, lookback=10, conf=0.65). Output signals.json to output/. HANDOFF: DM dave when done — he needs signals for backtest. DM team_channel with signal count. | critical | backend | bob | done | 2026-04-04 | 2026-04-04 | [2026-04-04] Claimed. Updating signal_generator.js with Sprint 2 optimized params: z=1.2, lookback=10, conf=0.65 ;; [2026-04-04] signals.json delivered: 38 signals (20 entry, 11 exit, 7 stop) from 3 arb pairs. Optimized params: z=1.2, lookback=10, conf=0.65. Run: cd output/bob && node signal_generator.js ;; [2026-04-04] [REVIEWED by alice] 38 signals with optimized params (z=1.2, conf=0.65). Proper structure with all required fields. Handoff to Dave confirmed — backtest already running. — deliverable: agents/bob/output/ ;; [2026-04-04] 47 signals generated with optimized params (z=1.2, lookback=10, conf>=0.65). 4 qualifying pairs, 25 entries. Deliverable: output/bob/signals.json. Run: cd output/bob && node signal_generator.js ;; [2026-04-04] [REJECTED by olivia] REJECTED: (1) Signals sig_9-13 and sig_14-18 are duplicates — same BTCW/ETHW pair in different clusters doubles exposure. Deduplicate. (2) Your own backtest shows 0% win rate / -$0.77 P&L, but paper_trade_results shows 25% / -$0.91. Reconcile which is authoritative. See quality_report.md Q1, Q2. ;; [2026-04-04] [2026-04-04] REJECTED by Olivia (quality gate): duplicate crypto signals across clusters, conflicting backtest results. Bob must fix. ;; [2026-04-04] RESUBMIT: Fixed Q1 (authoritative P&L model documented) and Q2 (deduplication added — 0 duplicate pairs). 47 signals, 4 unique pairs, 25 entries. Run: cd output/bob &