{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018bP5kwFM9V2BRZq3nJZ8aM","type":"tool_result","content":"# Sprint 4 Launched — Kalshi API Readiness\n\n**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)\n**Date:** 2026-04-04\n\nSprint 3 complete (10/10 approved). Launching Sprint 4: **prepare for real Kalshi data**.\n\n8 tasks created (T578-T585). Key assignments:\n- **Bob**: Kalshi API client (T578) — the foundation\n- **Grace**: Real market data integration (T579) — depends on Bob\n- **Dave**: Walk-forward backtest + position sizing (T580)\n- **Tina**: E2E test with realistic mocks (T583)\n- **Charlie**: Pipeline monitoring dashboard (T581)\n- **Heidi**: Credential security (T582)\n- **Olivia**: Quality gate (T584)\n- **Sam**: Velocity tracking (T585)\n\nCheck your tasks. DM me if blocked. Following D2, D5, C9.","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"48008a54-d595-43bc-b057-2930e8d16065","uuid":"db1c6d59-376e-4228-b029-4375d0cc8077","timestamp":"2026-04-04T19:26:11.396Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"# Sprint 4 Launched — Kalshi API Readiness\n\n**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)\n**Date:** 2026-04-04\n\nSprint 3 complete (10/10 approved). Launching Sprint 4: **prepare for real Kalshi data**.\n\n8 tasks created (T578-T585). Key assignments:\n- **Bob**: Kalshi API client (T578) — the foundation\n- **Grace**: Real market data integration (T579) — depends on Bob\n- **Dave**: Walk-forward backtest + position sizing (T580)\n- **Tina**: E2E test with realistic mocks (T583)\n- **Charlie**: Pipeline monitoring dashboard (T581)\n- **Heidi**: Credential security (T582)\n- **Olivia**: Quality gate (T584)\n- **Sam**: Velocity tracking (T585)\n\nCheck your tasks. DM me if blocked. Following D2, D5, C9.","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
