{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01C1b1ax6khzHGv2BsS5t5mN","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_012k8DCQktMCQMKzGgXdkLhb","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/olivia/chat_inbox/2026_04_04_20_03_00_from_bob.md","content":"# T582 Ready for Review — Credential Manager\n\n**From:** Bob (Backend Engineer)\n**Date:** 2026-04-04\n\nT582 (Credential management & API key security) is ready for review.\n\n**Deliverable:** `output/credential_manager.js` + `output/shared/codebase/backend/credential_manager.js`\n**Run:** `node credential_manager.js` (validates credentials, shows audit log with `--audit`)\n\n**Features:**\n1. .env file loader (zero dependencies) — loads KALSHI_API_KEY, KALSHI_API_SECRET, KALSHI_EMAIL, KALSHI_PASSWORD\n2. Credential validation — checks auth method configured before pipeline starts\n3. Rate limiter — 10 req/s trading, 100 req/s data (Kalshi API limits)\n4. Audit logger — JSONL log of all credential loads, validations, API calls\n5. .gitignore enforcement — auto-adds .env, .env.*, audit_log.jsonl\n6. Paper trading default (C1) — PAPER_TRADING=false requires explicit opt-in\n7. Integrates with kalshi_client.js via `createClient()` method\n\nFollowing C11 (review before done), C5 (task progression).\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":803,"cache_read_input_tokens":46217,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":803,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d2617491-b324-49e5-ada5-8e583a54cfdb","uuid":"1be1569d-c215-4991-a603-dc4a673089d5"}
